}}'''Belgium''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Brussels, along with Antwerp, Bruges, Ghent and Ostend.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with Belgium; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Djibouti]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Switzerland]], [[Taiwan]], [[Thailand]], [[United Arab Emirates]], and [[Uruguay]]. It was added to Android September 21, 2019 Belgium also has royalty when you play in Belgium there is a low choice you can be a Nobel or royal the nobility is duke and lower and the royalty is prince/princess 
